description: This app is pretty easy to use. All you do is ask Alexa to open Trump the Chump, or to "tell you a joke' and Alexa will run through a series of jokes about the Republican presidential candidate. When the cringe factor gets too high, you can tell Alexa to "stop".
exampleInteractions: 'Alexa, ask Trump the Chump to tell me a joke'
name: Trump the Chump
shortDescription: This is an app that tells tasteless jokes about Republican presidential candidate Donald J. Trump.
